%pig
diabetes = LOAD 'diabetes.csv' USING PigStorage(',') as (pregnancies:int, glucose:int, bloodpressure:int, skinThickness:int, Insulin:int, BMI:double, diabetesPedigreeFunction:double, age:int, outcome:int);

%pig.query

foreach diabetes generate pregnancies, glucose, bloodpressure, skinThickness, Insulin, BMI, diabetesPedigreeFunction, age, outcome;
